name: Imperial Arrest Order
Lore: 'When an Imperial blockade raises the alert level, all independent ships are scanned and any suspicious characters on planet are detained and interrogated.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Unique (•) Imperials of ability < 3 are forfeit +2. Nabrun Leids and Elis Helrot are limited to owner''s move phase and exterior sites. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
